To pulldown and work with our repo, first follow the instructions by android source at: http://source.android.com/source/initializing.html
to set up your machine
Then follow the instruction here: http://source.android.com/source/downloading.html replacing the repo init command with:
$ repo init -u https://github.com/TeamSourcery/platform_manifest.git -b jb
$ repo sync

after the repo sync, do not attempt to follow the aosp guidlines anymore, you've been sourcerized!

For 4.2  GSM and TORO

$ repo init -u https://github.com/TeamSourcery/platform_manifest.git -b jb4.2
$ repo sync

For 4.2 TOROPLUS

$ repo init -u https://github.com/TeamSourcery/platform_manifest.git -b jbplus
$ repo sync
